# Unreal Engine Project .gitignore

# --- Unreal Engine Generated Directories ---
# These contain compiled code and cached assets that are generated on-the-fly.
Binaries/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Saved/

# --- IDE/Editor Specific Directories ---
# Local settings for Visual Studio, Rider, VS Code, etc.
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Unreal Engine Build & Project Files ---
# These files are typically auto-generated by the engine from the .uproject file.
*.sln
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.filters
*.vcxproj.user
*.code-workspace

# --- OS Specific Files ---
# Ignore system-specific metadata
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Backup and Crash Reports ---
# We generally don't want to track crash logs or local backups in version control.
/Saved/Logs/
/Saved/Crashes/
/Saved/Backup/